_sText:
de_multidoor_tnk_v1
Inspired by multidoor
Once a 20-min idea, it then turned into something else
The map itself is a warehouse split into storage rooms, connected with rollup doors.
Healing stations give you 50hp and take time to recharge.
Bomb/defuse is just a default activity, the map itself is intended more for deathmatch or gungame.
The map uses a number of my own models, please don't steal.

Contact me via Steam if you need an edit.

Built by Tinker (formerly sub357)
Assistance and testing by Funny
